{"tid":424352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日搭地鐵番學見到啲廢老就嬲","createTime":"2017-10-04T15:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T15:08:27.000Z","uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e083a3b158537a50d20a50f48a534f4327c47853","tid":424352,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T15:07:19.000Z","msg":"今日搭地鐵番學見到啲廢老就嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時地鐵即使FULL晒人，關愛座都沒人敢坐。<br />\n今日見到啲廢老專係坐晒起一般座，但又唔座起關愛座，搞到個關愛座空晒，<br />\n周圍啲候生仔女包括我都唔敢坐落去，個陣我仲要好急屎，想搵個坐底⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我屌班廢老可唔可以第一時間坐起關愛座阿。"},{"pid":"e4e3dcae6a017c8fe7bd6aec691e627011306413","tid":424352,"uid":8302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"都唔坐得幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}